  "title": "Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><em><strong>We offer attractive benefits such as 5 days week, Flexible Work Arrangement, AWS, Variable Bonus etc. to successful candidate.</strong></em></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ol><li><strong>Configuration and Commissioning:</strong>Assist in the configuration and commission of Building Management System applications at client sites.<br />Ensure proper integration with existing building systems.</li><li><strong>Troubleshooting:</strong>Provide technical support for application-related issues, diagnosing and resolving problems in a timely manner.<br />Collaborate with the engineering team to escalate and resolve complex technical issues.</li><li><strong>Client Training:</strong>Conduct training sessions for clients on the use and maintenance of BMS/ELV applications.<br />Respond to client inquiries and provide guidance on application functionality.</li></ol><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ol><li>NITEC or Higher NITEC in Mechanical Engineering, Electrical Engineering, or Engineering related field.</li><li>Basic understanding of Building Management Systems and related technologies.</li><li>Strong problem-solving and communication skills</li></ol>",
